{
  "texts": [
    "Since DIC-Transformer is a two-stage method, the experiment mainly consists of two tasks:",
    "Faster R-CNN.",
    "Object detection backbone comparison experiments based on Faster R-CNN are implemented in two open-source frameworks, Detectron2 (Wu et al., 2019) and MMDetection (Chen et al., 2019).",
    "Detectron2 is a robust object detection platform developed by FAIR (Facebook AI Research) in 2019.",
    "Several state-of-the-art detection and segmentation algorithms are already integrated, eliminating the need to develop these networks from the ground up."
  ]
}